Break keyword is used to terminate the loop when encountered.
Means you are searching for an element when it occur print statement print that element and teminate that loop.

For Example :

num = [12,13,15,14,16,17,18,19,82,78,45,55,96,45,25,498,47,58,58,656,5656,5,285,5,58,5]
index = 0
search = 96
while index <= len(num) - 1:

  if num[index] == search:
    print("The element is found on the index -",index)
    break
  index = index + 1
print("End loop")
  
